comments.LineComment: | Implementation of the `PackageName` data type from the registry spec. A
| package name uniquely identifies a package.

value.value: Package name should start with a lower case char or a digit
Package names should not begin with 'purescript-'
Package names cannot contain consecutive dashes
Package name should end with a lower case char or digit
Package name can contain lower case chars, digits and non-consecutive dashes
Package name cannot be longer than 50 characters
